.TH MNEMOSYNE-INGEST-EXTRACT 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne ingest-extract \- Extract entities and relations from source files into the knowledge graph.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne ingest-extract\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Extract entities and relations from source files into the knowledge graph.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fBpath\fR
File or directory to extract from
.TP
\fB\-\-domain\fR
Domain for extraction (default: coding)
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR
Output format (default: json)
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\-id\fR
Attach a scope ID (e.g. session name) to extracted entities
.TP
\fB\-\-source\-channel\fR
Tag the extraction source channel (default: cli)
.TP
\fB\-\-examples\fR
Show extraction examples and output format details
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
